Folder Structure

guitar-learning-app/
├── CMakeLists.txt                  # Main CMake file
├── src/                            # Source code directory
│   ├── main.cpp                    # Application entry point
│   ├── audio/                      # Audio processing modules
│   │   ├── AudioCapture.h          # Audio input interface
│   │   ├── AudioCapture.cpp        # Audio capture implementation
│   │   ├── SignalProcessor.h       # Signal processing interface
│   │   └── SignalProcessor.cpp     # FFT and chromagram implementation
│   ├── chord/                      # Chord recognition modules
│   │   ├── ChordRecognizer.h       # Chord detection interface
│   │   └── ChordRecognizer.cpp     # Chord detection algorithms
│   ├── data/                       # Data management modules
│   │   ├── SongManager.h           # Song database interface
│   │   └── SongManager.cpp         # Song and chord storage
│   ├── gui/                        # User interface modules
│   │   ├── MainFrame.h             # Main window interface
│   │   ├── MainFrame.cpp           # UI implementation
│   │   ├── ChordDisplay.h          # Chord visualization component
│   │   └── ChordDisplay.cpp        # Visual chord representation
│   └── utils/                      # Utility functions
│       ├── Constants.h             # Application constants
│       └── Logger.h                # Logging utilities
├── resources/                      # Application resources
│   ├── chords/                     # Chord diagrams and images
│   │   ├── major/                  # Major chord diagrams
│   │   ├── minor/                  # Minor chord diagrams
│   │   └── seventh/                # 7th chord diagrams
│   └── icons/                      # Application icons
├── data/                           # Data storage directory
│   └── songs.db                    # SQLite database for songs
├── include/                        # Third-party headers
├── lib/                            # Third-party libraries
└── test/                           # Test files
    ├── TestAudioCapture.cpp
    ├── TestSignalProcessor.cpp
    └── TestChordRecognizer.cpp



    what to download

    Here's what you'll need to download and install:

Core C++ Development Tools:

CMake (build system): https://cmake.org/download/
A C++ compiler (GCC, Clang, or MSVC depending on your platform)
Git for version control: https://git-scm.com/downloads


Audio Processing Libraries:

PortAudio for real-time audio input: http://www.portaudio.com/download.html
FFTW for spectral analysis: http://www.fftw.org/download.html


GUI Framework (choose one):

Qt (comprehensive GUI framework): https://www.qt.io/download
wxWidgets (cross-platform GUI library): https://wxwidgets.org/downloads/


Additional Libraries:
SQLite for song database: https://www.sqlite.org/download.html
Eigen for matrix operations: https://eigen.tuxfamily.org/index.php?title=Main_Page
libsndfile for audio file handling: http://www.mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/#Download